Hello friends!

Taylor's birthday is next Wednesday, and they want to celebrate with a repeat of last year's amazing festivities!

What does that mean?

FOOD BOARD PARTY â€“ Part 2! ðŸ§€

When: Saturday, July 19, 2025, at 5:00 PM
Where: 123 Greenview Way, River City

Bring a creative and delicious charcuterie-style board! Get as fun and inventive as you like - sweet, savory, themed, or totally out-of-the-box!

No pressure, but we'll be voting again, and yes, there will be prizes! That said, just like last year, everyone is a winner because all the boards were incredible, and we all got to enjoy them!

One catch: Bonus points if Taylor can eat your board! Since they're pregnant, that means no deli meats, raw fish (sushi), steak, runny eggs, etc.

To keep things interesting, let everyone know what you're bringing so we don't end up with too many similar boards. A quick reply should do the trick! I'll wait to choose what we do once I get a sense of what everyone else is bringing.

We can't wait to see (and taste) what you come up with!

See you soon!
